==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Epizoöty
<hw>Ep`i*zo"⟦oum⟧*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧pizo⟦oum⟧tie</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A contagious
disease which attacks many animals at the same time; an epizootic
disease; an epidemic among animals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A murrain; an epidemic influenza among
horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Epoch</ent>⟦br⟧
